text: Emmanuelle Vaugier (born 23 June 1976) is a Canadian actress, musician and fashion model. She played Detective Jessica Angell on CSI: NY. She also played Mia on Two and a Half Men. She has also been in some movies. The actress was born in Vancouver, British Columbia. ==Reference== Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian movie actors Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Vancouver
